 to find a nunber at rth row and cth column in pascal triangle use n-1Cr-1 and use a for loop to calciulate the value instead of factorial 
to print a row you can use for loop from c=1 c<n and using the above function whuich takes a long time so use
 vector<int>list;
        int ans = 1;
        list.push_back(ans);
        for(int i=1;i<row;i++){
            ans = ans*(row-i);
            ans = ans/i;
            list.push_back(ans);
        }
        return list;
same can be used to print all the rows when a rownumber is given
